metadata.title: Protracted Section Grids (QMQ1)

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Alaska Department of Natural Resources, Division of Support Services-Land Records Information Section

metadata.description: Data Type: Base Maps  ;Section boundaries were generated using BLM, DNR, and U.S. Fish and Wildlife computer programs and township coordinate files for the construction of digital protracted sections. The programs make calculations from the radian measurements representing township corner coordinates. Protracted grid sections are available by ordering individual 1:250,000 quad sheets as templates.
